			<Para Align="" Color="" FontDefstyle="3" FontName="" FontSize="" FontStyle="" PromptObject="" SpacingBefore="1" TextMode="rich"><![CDATA[<DIV>Welcome to&nbsp;the web site of Alba Gas Ltd!<BR><BR>On this home page, we'll introduce our business and highlight important areas on our site. ]]><ButtonPlace/><![CDATA[</DIV>]]></Para>
		</Area>
