			<Para Align="" Color="" FontDefstyle="0" FontName="" FontSize="" FontStyle="" PromptObject="" SpacingBefore="1" TextMode="rich"><![CDATA[<DIV>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT size=3><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif color=#0066ff><EM>Alba Gas Limited are based in Govan, Glasgow.&nbsp; Our company is dedicated to serving the needs of our customers from being an approved Service / repair and Installation partner with Scottish Gas to Private Landlords, Housing Associations and to one-off private&nbsp;customers. </EM></FONT></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT size=3><EM><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif><FONT color=#0066ff>&nbsp;<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" ?><o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></EM></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif color=#0066ff size=3><EM>The Alba Gas Senior Management Team has gained a wealth of experience from&nbsp;over 60&nbsp;years working in the Gas Industry.&nbsp; We can deliver custom made packages covering all types of Central Heating Design, Boiler Servicing / Repairs, Installations (Gas &amp; Electric) and a Quality Assurance Service.<SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </SPAN>Our reputation for Quality and Safety has now been adopted by other skills that we offer, namely Disabled Adaptations, Plumbing and Electrical work.</EM></FONT></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif color=#0066ff size=3><EM></EM></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif color=#0066ff><EM>All of our employees are fully qualified in their relevant trades.&nbsp; We are CORGI registered and employ surveyors, auditors, gas service engineers, installation engineers and electricians. Our two Senior Managers are formally training instructors within the gas industry which reflects in the standard of workmanship that Alba Gas employees produce.</EM></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif color=#0066ff><EM></EM></FONT></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><FONT face=Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif color=#0066ff><EM>We firmly believe that our employees are our greatest asset, therefore their training and well being are foremost in our minds.</EM></FONT>&nbsp;</SPAN>]]><ButtonPlace/><![CDATA[</P></DIV>]]></Para>
